UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc1='전 깡총 군이랑 산책하러 나왔는데 중간에 길을 잃어버렸어요. 게다가 늑대들이 막 쫓아와서 너무 무서웠어요. 다행히 이 탑이 보여서 저랑 깡총 군이랑 이 안에 숨은 거예요. 늑대들은 결국 다 사라졌는데, 정말 무서웠고요, 우린 이제 집에 돌아가는 길도 몰라요.',Text0_1_loc1='전 깡총 군이랑 산책하러 나왔는데 중간에 길을 잃어버렸어요. 게다가 늑대들이 막 쫓아와서 너무 무서웠어요. 다행히 이 탑이 보여서 저랑 깡총 군이랑 이 안에 숨은 거예요. 늑대들은 결국 다 사라졌는데, 정말 무서웠고요, 우린 이제 집에 돌아가는 길도 몰라요.' WHERE entry=13023; /* Text0_0: Mr. Floppy and I went for a walk, but then we got lost and I was really scared, cause there were these wolves, you know, and they chased us, but then I saw this tower and Mr. Floppy and I hid here and the wolves finally went away after a while and it was terrible and now we don\'t know how to get back home. */ /* Text0_1: Mr. Floppy and I went for a walk, but then we got lost and I was really scared, cause there were these wolves, you know, and they chased us, but then I saw this tower and Mr. Floppy and I hid here and the wolves finally went away after a while and it was terrible and now we don\'t know how to get back home. */
